Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.82,Default - Apostle,Dead,0,0,0,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.33,Default - Apostle,Dead,0,0,0,,Give back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.53,Default - Apostle,Dead,0,0,0,,My warm body...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.50,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:31.30,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.51,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,It's getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.51,Title,Sign 0042,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,259)}A Nighttime Feast: Burning at the Stake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.09,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.29,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I knew it, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.06,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:29.43,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,He took off without me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:30.54,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,He won't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.01,Default,P,0,0,0,,Hey, we've been on the move since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:46.03,Default,P,0,0,0,,If you don't rest, you'll be exhausted \Nwhen we reach our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.59,Default,P,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.77,Default,P,0,0,0,,His nasty looks and stubbornness kind \Nof reminded me of you, Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.90,Default,G,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.39,Default,P,0,0,0,,No sudden stops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.86,Default,P,0,0,0,,Be more considerate of your host!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.03,Default,P,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.14,Default,G,0,0,0,,Someone I've known for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.75,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,You look to be in good health, Struggler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.62,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,An elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.69,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,An interesting choice of companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.84,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.26,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,He's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.87,Default,G,0,0,0,,Been a while, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.62,Default,G,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.41,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,I am a foe to otherworldly beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:33.19,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,You will soon learn what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.69,Default,G,0,0,0,,There's an Apostle nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.51,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Or their root cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.12,Default,G,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.29,Default,G,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.20,Default,G,0,0,0,,The God Hand is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:48.58,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,Did you not also see the shining \Nhawk in your dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:51.12,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,That was a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:58.41,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,That someone, who signifies the hawk, \Nwill appear in this mortal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.98,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,The hawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.21,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,The hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.70,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,The flocks of sheep are being guided \Nto a blood-stained holy land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.99,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,What they seek is a hawk of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:13.17,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,When the place of power attains a critical \Nthreshold, what normally lies in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.98,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,the realm of gods is incarnated, \Nonce every thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:21.43,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,You and the girl will find yourselves \Nthrown into that maelstrom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.57,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,as though tracing a passage through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.78,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,The Eclipse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.12,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,An event similar to the Eclipse is about to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.15,Default,G,0,0,0,,It's about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,It's going to happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.14,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,Joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:56.40,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no man possesses the means \Nto change this festival's outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.71,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,A shadow will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:04.53,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,It will simply be a shadow cast by a dying \Nsun that shines on a faraway land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:08.19,Default,G,0,0,0,,You're saying the outcome will \Nbe the same as last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.35,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,That we are both here, without meaning to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.30,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,is proof beyond reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:16.98,Default - Apostle,Skelle,0,0,0,,We are already caught in the whorls of karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:22.73,Default,G,0,0,0,,Shadows, karma... Like I give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.75,Default,G,0,0,0,,In the past, I borrowed your powers, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:31.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,But this time, I will draw on my \Nown strength to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.77,Default,G,0,0,0,,And I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:40.50,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Perhaps that brand will be of assistance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.59,Default,G,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.99,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,A word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.83,Default - Apostle,Skele,0,0,0,,Do not have more than\None that you care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:23.33,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Man, what is our holy commander thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:26.49,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Why is she kissing up to Father Mozgus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.93,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Yeah, she sure has some noble faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.82,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Hey, she can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.02,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.32,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Please be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.85,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.37,Default,F,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.90,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Why is a klutz like him the officer of arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.81,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:49.84,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Because he wags his tail and falls over \Nhimself to please her, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.47,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Anyway, we have even more of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.51,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,More what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.98,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.92,Default,F,0,0,0,,A-Ah, where is Father Mozgus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.31,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I will come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.67,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I was just on my way to the chapel to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.25,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Did we shock you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.51,Default,F,0,0,0,,Er, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:39.23,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,All of us have been persecuted \Nbecause of our appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.03,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Exiled from villages and towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.05,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,we were reviled as monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.55,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Some even lived in hiding, in the forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.24,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Please look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.58,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I was born with a rare disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.94,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Without this mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.05,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I'd be burned all over my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.38,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even look human anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:15.20,Default - flashback,Moz,0,0,0,,God, I thank you for bringing us \Nhere today in a fateful act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:20.39,Default - flashback,Moz,0,0,0,,Child of fate, find pride and \Nfaith within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.29,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I do not like my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.96,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,I cannot find it within myself \Nto enjoy hurting others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.90,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,But still, I am proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:34.55,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,For this is a holy task given to me by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.65,Default,F,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.68,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,It is the sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.91,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,my master's worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.48,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Prostration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.19,Default,F,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.30,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Every day, morning and evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.43,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,Father Mozgus prostrates himself \Nbefore God a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.68,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,In the past decade, he hasn't \Nfailed to do so even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.95,Default,Crow,0,0,0,,He seems to be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.86,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Well met, Lady Farnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.09,Default,F,0,0,0,,Father Mozgus, you're bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.62,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.49,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,This tower is a most sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:25.14,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,A holy man, imprisoned here \Nby the conqueror Gaiseric,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.15,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,continued to recount the king's sins \Nto God, even while being tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:35.01,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Eventually, in response to his pleas, \Nan angel is said to have descended.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:39.24,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I cannot help but be more devout \Nin my worship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:41.66,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:45.28,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Because of these wounds, I can barely walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.38,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,I can run no longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:52.15,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,But I am fond of this agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.71,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,My holy mission is to enforce God's stern law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:02.16,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Regrettably, that means causing agony to many.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:05.27,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,These wounds are admonitions to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.67,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,as well as proof of my faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.56,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Are you having some kind of doubts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.03,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am simply unsure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.05,Default,F,0,0,0,,Will this mission allow us to save people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:21.28,Default,F,0,0,0,,The common people bear us only ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.38,Default,F,0,0,0,,And though it shames me to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:28.07,Default,F,0,0,0,,even some among my Holy Iron Chain \NKnights oppose this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.35,Default,F,0,0,0,,Please dismiss this as a mere initiate's ramblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:35.80,Default,F,0,0,0,,But I fear that continuing this way will \Nmean that terror spreads unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.57,Default,F,0,0,0,,exhausting the people's hearts and minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.91,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,You must not deplore difficult tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.23,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,You must not question God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.02,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,Though you may endure bloodshed, \Nin both mind and body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.99,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,you must continue to live for God's glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.72,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,That is faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:03.47,Default,Moz,0,0,0,,It is for God, and God alone, that we act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.74,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,For God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.77,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,And God alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.74,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,For God alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.08,Default,Gran,0,0,0,,Thank you for always doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.63,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.46,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Hey, Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.94,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't get yourself \Nall muddy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.47,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,N-Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.01,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Joachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.63,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.73,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Don't you know what's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.23,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.69,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Or are you saying you still want my \Nservices, even though you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.99,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:04.74,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I'm just worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.58,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:11.18,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that I can't lie with \Nyou, even if you're nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.65,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Oh, but that's not what I meant—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.00,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Then try to screw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.69,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.92,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,If you think you're that brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.50,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,come to the riverbank tonight, \Nwhen the midnight bell tolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.80,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,What's going on, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.61,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Why all the racket so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.44,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.83,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.25,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:09.93,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Then, are you willing to be \Ndamned to Hell with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.48,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.49,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,This isn't for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.31,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,That girl. Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.33,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Come, let's go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.09,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,I knew it. That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.09,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,This makes you hallucinate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.01,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Now, let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.53,Default,Cultist,0,0,0,,The goddess of flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.17,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.04,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Come, Joachim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.30,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Oh, Great Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.07,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,please convert this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.31,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Now, drink this, and become one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.24,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Joachim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.52,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.49,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.16,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,He'll expose us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.47,Default,Cultist,0,0,0,,He can't have survived from this height.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.17,Default,Cultist,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.85,Default,Cultist,0,0,0,,People might come because of the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.48,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Yeah, right... Liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.52,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.03,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.02,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,No, stay away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.77,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:17.27,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.49,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.98,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:32.14,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I've always hated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:35.39,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Always acting like a know-it-all, \Nordering us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.97,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I bet you feel good about yourself, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:42.81,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,You're a whore, just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.47,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.73,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,How can you look down on others like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.20,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I-If I scream, my people will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.99,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,You'll be torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.62,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.17,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.01,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.12,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.58,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.31,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.68,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,You worried me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.65,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,You stupid girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.44,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.66,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Joachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.57,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Don't talk right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.62,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.62,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Hey, she's a whore with Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.81,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the crazy one who's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.92,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.75,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Elai—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.88,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,That girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.51,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Hey, show us your rotting face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.19,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.28,Default,Men,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.55,Default,Men,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:02.51,Default,Men,0,0,0,,She's a real beauty, once you \Nlook under the bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.49,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Yeah, struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.85,Default,Men,0,0,0,,It's more fun when they fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.65,Default,Men,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.65,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.66,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.15,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.84,Default,Men,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.29,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.13,Default - Apostle,Men,0,0,0,,Starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.57,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.75,Default - Apostle,Cultist,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.09,Default - Apostle,Cultist,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.43,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Elaine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.86,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Elaine, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.73,Default,Men,0,0,0,,A witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.86,Default,Men,0,0,0,,She's a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.39,Default,F,0,0,0,,Light the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.63,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,She's sure into this whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.85,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I heard the commander's family home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:01.55,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,was right at a burning ground for heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:05.22,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Since she was a young girl, she's willingly lit fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.90,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I heard she was allowed to search \Nfor the Black Swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:12.68,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,because three years ago, she caught \Nheretics plotting to rebel against
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:16.46,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,the Holy See and burned them all at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.68,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,So she's born and bred that way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.67,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,I should stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.65,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,You, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.29,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,No small talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:25.09,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.64,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.71,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Brat, you're a heretic, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.68,Default,Man,0,0,0,,The son of a heretic is also a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.59,Default,Man,0,0,0,,If not, throw this onto the pyre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.61,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:41.32,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,That child is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.15,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,We investigated him when \Nwe questioned the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.06,Default,Man,0,0,0,,M-My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:47.95,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.21,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to obligate you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:05.13,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.72,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Lord Jerome, I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:12.19,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,Oh, you aren't the officer of arms \Nfor nothing. Good memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.73,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,You're not so bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.48,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.27,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,That kid back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.07,Default,Jerome,0,0,0,,That was nice knightly behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.53,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.49,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,You see, it's personal for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.49,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,I was just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:32.43,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,My mother was also burned \Nat the stake as a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:35.87,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Three years ago, before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:40.35,Default - italics,Jerome,0,0,0,,Three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:05.48,Default - flashback,Shadows,0,0,0,,Good work, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:06.33,Default - flashback,Shadows,0,0,0,,Bless her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:08.36,Default - flashback,Shadows,0,0,0,,God bless her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:22.91,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:31.50,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.38,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,That monster never gets tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:38.16,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I've finally caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:49.94,Default,G,0,0,0,,Casca...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:01.39,Title,Sign 2358,0,0,0,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.42,EndInsert,Sign 2404,0,0,0,,Giving up before the job's done? No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.51,EndInsert,Sign 2408,0,0,0,,We have come to welcome you, Lady Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:13.47,EndInsert,Sign 2412,0,0,0,,I kind of have the advantage here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:17.47,EndInsert,Sign 2416,0,0,0,,Go crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.48,EndInsert,Sign 2420,0,0,0,,You call this a holy land?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:27.40,Title2,Sign 2425,0,0,0,,Next Episode \NThe Black Witch
